body:
Hi Chris, This is the rookie question and I apologize. I downloaded the example Mostapha shared in the new version announcement. Somehow the air gap material doesn't exist in the library. I tried going over the available materials and it wasn't there. Now this is not bug ofc, as the whole thing works when I change it to anything in the library. But the air gap would be an important material to have in these. I wonder if it is my fault missing this or I need to create one with the components?
Sorry for taking your time about this small matter. Kind regards, Theodore.
